						<visible>[[Container(300).HasFocus(1) + !ControlGroup(3900).HasFocus()]] | [Container(3900).HasNext + ControlGroup(3900).HasFocus()] | [[Container(300).HasFocus(2) + !ControlGroup(3800).HasFocus()]] | [Container(3800).HasNext + ControlGroup(3800).HasFocus()]</visible>
